  RIPscrip v2.0 Server-Side Rendering Engine
  ============================================
  Mystic BBS IRC Fork — rip2api.pas
  5,304 lines | 67 commands | 170 methods
  256-color | 1280x1024 | RFF scalable fonts

  Backward-compatible v1.54 + v2.0 extensions:
  Configurable resolution (320x200-1280x1024)
  256-color palette, extended polyline/polygon
  RFF font loading, JPEG/BMP/PAL support
  3D transforms, sprites, Wu antialiasing
  Palette fade/rotate, block resize/rotate
  WAV streaming + PNG + JPEG streaming

  Codec: img/ (JPEG decoder + pasjpeg)
  Pure Pascal | Zero dependencies
  FPC 2.6.4irc | All platforms | GPLv3
  Tests: 115/115 (2 suites)

  Part of the Mystic BBS IRC Fork
  July 2026
